  "description": "<p>Location: Paragon & Takashimaya<br />Basic + AWS + Commission + VB<br /></p><p><strong>Job scope: </strong></p><ul><li>Sales and budget, retail operations and administration, customer service, merchandising and promotions</li><li>Accuracy of all receipts.</li><li>Maintain good customer relationship and regular updates of products to customers.</li><li>Ensure good housekeeping of stores.</li><li>Ensures the stock model, according to the guidelines set by the Company and carry out inventories according to the established periodicity.</li><li>Collaborate to achieve the sales target.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p><ul><li>Min “O-level” in education</li><li>Min 2 years in retail </li><li>Great communication skills</li></ul><p><br /><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please click on <strong>“Apply Now”</strong>\nor email <strong>ref44@trustrecruit.com.sg</strong></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to\nsafeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection\nAct (PDPA). </p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website www.trustrecruit.com.sg.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Lim Wei Jye (Jaylyn)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24121213</p>",
